scenes.description: Mori Calliope and Koseki Bijou perform 'Stellar Stellar' in a crystalline cavern setting.
Mori Calliope and Ouro Kronii perform 'Wanted, Wasted' on a stage surrounded by statues.
Mori Calliope speaks to the audience (MC section) about the production and the set design.
